race.description: Trio Sign Group (N/P) Stake Pr1 Division1
race.comment: ALL THE SASS (2) latest effort finished 3rd on November 12 over 400m at this track behind Fantastic Tommy beaten 3.5 lengths (23.08) in a Other. Looks well placed and should feature. NO FINES (7) has missed the placings at her last couple but was in the money three back when third (23.31) at this track in a Other. Expected to bounce back to best. SPLIT VISION (4) settled close to the lead but checked in the run and turned spotting a start, missing the frame when fourth (23.37) at this track over 400m in a Other. Bold showing expected on best. HUXI BEAR (8) cannot be written off despite a miss here at his latest outing.
